Reasoning: 
1. cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with the data complexity of model-checking for logics with team semantics. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses the complexity of logical formulas, which is relevant to AI applications. 
3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is another possible category as the paper deals with the complexity of model-checking algorithms. 
4. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is relevant as the paper discusses the tractability/intractability frontier of data complexity. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with logical formulas, which are relevant to some machine learning applications.
